This is a midi controller using Raspberry Pi. Written in python. Used to be pedal looper project but removed all the looper / switcher parts and only use midi now.

to take picture with pi can and display on oled screen
$ raspistill -o image.jpg
$ pi@raspberrypi:~ $ python
  Python 2.7.16 (default, Oct 10 2019, 22:02:15)
  [GCC 8.3.0] on linux2
  Type "help", "copyright", "credits" or "license" for more information.
  >>> from PIL import Image
  >>> image = Image.open('image.jpg')
  >>> new_image = image.resize((128, 64))
  >>> new_image.save('new_image.ppm')
$ python /home/pi/Adafruit_Python_SSD1306/examples/image.py